description: ISO is an independent, non-governmental international organization with a membership of 163 national standards bodies. Data for concordance values is sourced from Statoids. Who's On First tracks which 'country' a feature belongs to via the 'wof:country' and 'iso:country' properties. No other ISO properties are referenced.
